Displacement versus time plots for atoms throughout the trajectory

The files included in this directory are: 

process/		directory used to process atom wise displacement
README			this file
dispVSframe.sh		creates displacement versus frame plots		
unpbc.sh		takes care of periodic boundry conditions(PBC)
sign.awk		function to remove the effect of PBC on displacement
input.sh 		collects input from the user required for the process

For more details, you can refer to the individual files.
